<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink131-kilavi">
        vāyil vēṇṭi vanta pāṇaṉ talaimakaṉ kātaṉmai kūṟiṉāṉākat talaimakaḷ vāyilmaṟuppāḷ avaṟkuk kūṟiyatu</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the heroine to him - the bard - as one who denies entry, the bard who came, hoping to enter speaking of the affection of the hero.
 </p>
            </div>  
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink131">
<l>naṉṟē pāṇa koṇkaṉatu naṭpē</l>
<l>tillai vēli yivvūrk</l>
<l>kalleṉ kauvai yeḻāak kālē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh bard, the friendship of the man from the maritime tract is good indeed,</l>
    <l>As long as loud gossip does not rise</l>
    <l>In this town that is surrounded with Tillai trees.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
